<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA49">
<l>malaiyēḻu mānilaṅka ḷēḻu matira</l>
<l>kulaicūḻ kuraikaṭalka ḷēḻu – mulaicūḻnta</l>
<l>nañcurattup peṇṇai naviṉṟuṇṭa nāvaṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟañcāteṉ ṉeñcē yaḻai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The seven mountains and the seven great continents and the seven noisy seas,</l>
<l>that thunderingly surround the banks, invoke, my heart,</l>
<l>without being afraid, as the One with a tongue that, prattling to the woman,</l>
<l>drank [her life] force along with the poison contained in [her] breast.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
